&trans     	&none	&kp LEFT  	&kp DOWN 	&kp RIGHT 	&kp PG_DN	                        &kp LEFT  	&kp DOWN 	&kp RIGHT 	        &none	    &bootloader	&trans
	                &trans      &trans      &trans      &trans  	&trans   	&trans  	&trans    	        &trans    	&trans   	&trans	

